     <div id="doctitlediv" class="wztit  mip-360doc-script-tit">
      澳门赌场！赌城！让我慢慢走向死亡边缘.(赌博的惨痛经历）！！！
     </div> 
     <div class="mainbox"> 
      <div class="time wzmas">
       <span id="savedatespan">16-03-16</span>
       <span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>
       <span id="resavename" class="name1"><a href="http://www.360doc.cn/userhome.aspx?userid=18668800" target="_blank">peter49</a></span>
       <span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>
       <a href="http://www.360doc.cn/login.aspx?url=http://www.360doc.cn/article/18668800_542632948.html&amp;addfollow=2&amp;url2=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.360doc.cn%2Findex.html" id="addcurrfollow" class="jgz mip-360doc-script-gz1" target="_blank"><b class="fontb14">+</b>&nbsp;关注</a>
       <a href="http://www.360doc.cn/login.aspx?url=http://www.360doc.cn/article/18668800_542632948.html&amp;loginflag=2&amp;url2=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.360doc.cn%2Findex.html" id="flowernum" class="jgz mip-360doc-script-xh1 xh" target="_blank">献花(0)</a>&nbsp;
       <a href="http://www.360doc.cn/login.aspx?url=http://www.360doc.cn/resavecategory.aspx?artid=542632948&amp;userid=18668800&amp;url2=http://www.360doc.cn/index.html" id="resaveid" class="jgz mip-360doc-script-p_header_sc" target="_blank">收藏</a>
